Type: Package
Package: smoothqr
Title: Smooth Multi-period Quantile Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel J.", "McDonald", , "daniel@stat.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Elena", "Tuzhilina", , "elena.tuzhilina@utoronto.ca", role = "aut")
  )
Description: This package estimates multi-reponse quantile regression in
    the context that the resulting predictions should be "smooth". The
    typical use case would be multi-horizon time-series forecasting
    wherein we believe that the responses should vary smoothly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://dajmcdon.github.io/smoothqr/
